title: The Rolling Stones - From The Vault - Marquee Club Live in 1971
description:
A very fine high quality release - a Rolling Stones show not in a stadium, but in the small and famous Marquee Club.
The Japanese release includes also as another famous show, first time officially released on CD - Live in the Forest National Arena, Brussels, on October 17, 1973. This stuff was previously only released as an official vinyl LP or as unofficial bootlegs ("Nasty Music" a.k.a. "Brussels Affair" a.k.a. "Bedspring Symphony" and some more...).
